{"tid":1810883,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【撼嬴姜濤】邵氏兄弟新簽5大爆肌男　何超蓮裕美前度最吸睛","createTime":"2020-01-04T08:42:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T19:21:30.000Z","uid":324078,"like":3,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"fa9c7d31f6d89b676cecdaaa9b53010f495e455f","tid":1810883,"uid":324078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T08:42:03.000Z","msg":"ViuTV大型選秀節目《全民造星》贏盡口碑，更掀起追星熱潮。當大家正熱烈討論《全民造星》的姜濤和剛出爐第二季冠軍吳啟洋（Phoebus）之際，原來邵氏旗下都有一眾勁吸睛，又大隻的小鮮肉，他們的潛力絕對不能忽視。<br />\n<br />\n邵氏兄弟國際影業有限公司的新人藝人中，不乏大隻仔，執行董事樂易玲指：「吸納新人唔一定係大隻仔，最緊要係覺得佢trainable（可造之材）。我哋需要電影啲嘅面孔，簽嘅人大部分做開電影。」邵氏旗下男藝人當中，最為人熟悉的便定是沈震軒（Sammy），他在《喜愛夜蒲2》中擔當「蘭桂坊USB」非常出位，之後更得到經理人黃柏高賞識，成為歌、影、視三棲藝人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/412752/多圖-邵氏兄弟新簽5大爆肌男-何超蓮前度最吸睛\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%2F412752%2F%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%96-%E9%82%B5%E6%B0%8F%E5%85%84%E5%BC%9F%E6%96%B0%E7%B0%BD5%E5%A4%A7%E7%88%86%E8%82%8C%E7%94%B7-%E4%BD%95%E8%B6%85%E8%93%AE%E5%89%8D%E5%BA%A6%E6%9C%80%E5%90%B8%E7%9D%9B&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDugAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=80f48a0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/412752/多圖-邵氏兄弟新簽5大爆肌男-何超蓮前度最吸睛</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSammy成日操肌，勁大隻。（IG/ @sammysumchunhin）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oYbpFbs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoYbpFbs.jpg&h=f84d5a4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來到邵氏新人方面，為大家介紹4位高顏值、潛力無限的爆肌男。第一位是李爾晨（Kyle），Kyle是模特兒，更是香港甲一男子排球員。2016年曾代表香港參選「國際先生」比賽，之後接拍電視劇、電影，仲有參演舞台劇，幕前經驗十分豐富。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0TYWwiz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0TYWwiz.jpg&h=1ec921f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKyle是一名運動員，要保持fit爆身型。（IG/ @kyleleeyisun）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mAG1Hqg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmAG1Hqg.jpg&h=1306f047&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y5PKFeU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY5PKFeU.jpg&h=97315430&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二位是模特兒出身的黃俊豪（Jeremy），他曾與賭王千金何超蓮拍拖。Jeremy憑健碩身材、英俊外表成為廣告界寵兒。2019年接拍網劇，亦有到馬來西亞參演綜藝節目。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/04/162758_6780a03d105b1bfc3939371e1a27b155.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F04%2F162758_6780a03d105b1bfc3939371e1a27b155.jpeg&h=19b8f190&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nModel出身的Jeremy外表有型。（IG/ @jeremixmatch）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/04/162801_bebde6a8fe62d297f12052652821db35.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F04%2F162801_bebde6a8fe62d297f12052652821db35.jpeg&h=62615f9e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UMzbkeZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUMzbkeZ.jpg&h=316772f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第三位是王志康（Hiroki），他曾參加《全民造星I》可惜落敗。現時為TVB藝人，擔任娛樂新聞台主播。Hiroki於日本東京國際大學畢業，對日本文化十分熟悉，他以旅遊達人名義寫專欄分享遊日經歷，去年有報告指與裕美蜜遊日本，繼而傳出緋聞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JO11HrR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJO11HrR.jpg&h=7e9e6b27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHiroki都係一名大隻仔，現在擔任娛樂新聞台主播。（IG/ @hirokihong）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qUPR4Fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqUPR4Fd.jpg&h=b2e3aaee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1LOvAOo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1LOvAOo.jpg&h=69a89b24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第四位是吳卓衡（Keefe），今年22歲的他於2017年加入TVB同是亦簽約邵氏，曾經參演劇集《愛‧回家之開心速遞》及《解決師》。Keefe年紀輕輕，潛能一定是無可限量。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NDssC0Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNDssC0Y.jpg&h=87691efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKeefe斯斯文文，但原來都好大隻。（IG/ @keefe_ng）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MOGkX0Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMOGkX0Z.jpg&h=4e1ad18f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KE5h0e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKE5h0e8.jpg&h=b52f620e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd67ad6fbd869e4c1bfa8aefdbb71da0f950de99","tid":1810883,"uid":28131,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T08:42:48.000Z","msg":"好gay個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00d5279ada173521812a59e5c7550bde4e4ddb7","tid":1810883,"uid":3189,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T08:43:46.000Z","msg":"簽藝人定簽鴨仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f59e1f8eb35882dd4a84b551d26f14c9ecd4d46","tid":1810883,"uid":61660,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"a00d5279ada173521812a59e5c7550bde4e4ddb7","tid":1810883,"uid":3189,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T08:43:46.000Z","msg":"簽藝人定簽鴨仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T08:44:42.000Z","msg":"執行董事樂易玲"},{"pid":"19ef1bcde87b67c35624f5bef67cb238da4cec76","tid":1810883,"uid":263183,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T08:45:58.000Z","msg":"前3件ok Last兩件好核突"},{"pid":"c902e5ff2a4049c13f762f92e413c8f71ca982d3","tid":1810883,"uid":40789,"like":0,"dislike":0